    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Reliable \u2014 A Great Everyday Driver! If you're looking for a dependable used car that won't let you down, this one deserves a look! In good condition overall, it presents well with a respectable exterior and a clean, functional interior. It drives smoothly and has been maintained, making it a trustworthy choice for daily commuting or family use. There are minor signs of normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of a great ownership experience. Come take it for a spin \u2014 you'll appreciate what good condition really means!",
