    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Dependable & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Solid Good-Condition Find!** Here's a great opportunity to own a well-maintained vehicle that's genuinely ready for the road! This car is in good condition \u2014 you'll notice the expected minor signs of normal use, like light interior wear and small cosmetic blemishes, but nothing that affects performance or reliability. It runs smoothly, drives confidently, and has been kept in solid shape throughout its life. If you're looking for a trustworthy everyday driver without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle, this one deserves a serious look! \ud83d\ude4c",
